hungry all the time so i've just discovered that i am pregnant yesterday is my mind playing tricks on me or am i supposed to be starving at all hours of the day i want to sleep but i am so hungry i eat but then i get hungry all over again gah help oh my goodness in response to the st answer i've been sick all afternoon i'm not throwing up but it feels like i'm going to so i sit in front of the toilet and wait and wait and then the feeling subsides and i'm just hungry oh yes the joys of pregnancy lol yes you may experience being hungry you may find that you are hungry even though you want to throw up i pretty much lived in the bathroom for the first trimester of both pregnancies but if i wasn't in the bathroom or in bed sleeping i was eating i just felt like about minutes after eating that i hadn't actually ate anything i had to carry snacks in my purse and kept eating at work i was amazed at how hungry i was even when i wanted to throw up i even dreamed about food lol Pregnancy Shaggy dog story EastEnders Married... with Children The Cure Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Obstetrics Miscarriage Episodes of Lost (Season 2) The Amazing Race Time Out of Mind Abortion Abortion debate One Tree Hill (TV series) One Piece minor characters Singlish Knots Landing Fasting Toilet humour Fecal incontinence Avenue Q Paul Is Dead Good Times Meal Blood Simple Baldrick Guinea pig Homer Simpson The Shining (film) Hey Jude Garfield Friends IBM PC compatible Arnold Rimmer Night (book) Days of our Lives Cliff Richard Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Insomnia Cat Fertility awareness History of As the World Turns (2000-present) Jacob Kurt Cobain Iditarod Characters in the Smurfs The Amazing Maurice and his Educated Rodents Elvis Presley Kibbutz Binge eating disorder Ron and Fez Melanie Wilkes Elephant Sex segregation AFI 100 Years series Marie Antoinette The Amber Spyglass Faith (Buffy the Vampire Slayer) Japanese toilet Jon Secada Lycanthropy Dutch S